  "text": "Here we were using the expression of F i in [CITATION_1] Lem. B.6 ]. Now it is not hard to show I 1 + I 2 > 0 for n > 4 + 2γ and γ ∈ (1, min{2, n/2}). Consequently, C 4 > 0. is defined in (2.26) and |S 6 | is the volume of 6 dimensional sphere.",
